              <span id="reviewTextContainer2459715759" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16825470873122410874">I felt I was reading history, turns out it was historical imagination so well wrought that it fit my foot. It’s a Me too, it’s a love story, it’s deep, it’s sexy, it’s world of fables explained through the eyes of a cinder girl. Wild mustangs couldn’t pull me away from this wonderful book.</span>

          </span>
