    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2290555709" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9493109856380573161">Ms. Velmans’ unique and inventive take is sure to appeal to readers of fantasy and historical fiction alike. Curious minds will also appreciate the mingling of real-life figures, such as Perrault (an important historical figure who hasn’t received much attention), with fairytale characters.<br/></span>

          </span>
        </div>


